    value: 10.5281/zenodo.21327845
    description: "Concept DOI resolving to the latest archived release (all versions)"
keywords:
  - bifurcation analysis
  - dynamical systems
  - numerical continuation
  - Lyapunov exponent
  - Poincaré map
  - chaos
  - Julia
